    "rationale": "Overall credibility is sufficient for the intended regulatory use. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single gap in Test conditions (achieved 2 vs required 3) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 is the established regulatory standard for spinal construct mechanical evaluation and no additional test conditions are required by FDA guidance. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance bounds.",
